data.description: Redone in 2022, this 3 bed 1 bath cottage is within walking distance to downtown, shops, and a block from the Spanish Moss Trail. New cabinets and appliances in the kitchen, an updated bath, new flooring, new wiring, new duck work, new windows, new insulation  and siding make this a brand new home. The large backyard has a new 8x12 work shed and offers views of the downtown fireworks. Seller to give $6500 for new roof with acceptable offer.Owner is listing agent.
